{
  "stem": "15174.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that he gave them the information that-- of what was going on, that the JDC had sent a representative, that he was making representations to the Cuban government and so on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and then, of course, these people on the committee would then go back to all the passengers and disseminate the information.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, the information would try to keep everybody a little upbeat anyway, because-- because people were terribly depressed, terribly scared, and they were afraid that there would be a wave of suicides.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, none of the negotiations were-- was successful, apparently, because a week later, I believe it was on the 31st-- no, it was June 1st, I think, we started sailing out of Havana Harbor.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know if you can imagine what people felt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, here we were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had left Germany where it was so terrible, and here we were, you know, a few hundred feet away from safety.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we weren't being allowed to land there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, you know, there was-- the mood on the ship was horrible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And people did threaten to commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and so the Captain apparently told the-- this committee, the passengers, that what he would do was not sail directly back to Havana-- I'm sorry-- back to Hamburg, but that he would sail along the coast of Florida.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And while more negotiations were going on with Cuba, so that maybe Cuba would change its mind, and we could just go back there, and also that we could make representations by telegram and so on to the United States government as well as other governments in the-- in the Western Hemisphere.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
